      "date": "2014-12-29 19:14:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWhy not use libcfs_nid2str_r() to implement libcfs_nid2str()?\n\n \nchar *libcfs_nid2str(lnet_nid_t nid)\n{\n        return libcfs_nid2str_r(nid, libcfs_next_nidstring(), LNET_NIDSTR_SIZE);\n}\n\nThen assume that libcfs_nid2str_r() is always passed a non-NULL buffer. This avoids the duplication of logic between these pairs of functions.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
